  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    GC Christmas webinar: Sustainable Chemistry
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">In this webinar, Professor Tom Welton will look at how sustainable chemistry is essential to achieve global sustainable development goals</p>

  </div>
</div>

