  <img class="app-c-figure__image" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/image_data/file/109796/s300_SDGs_2_Gov.uk.jpg" alt="Professor Tom Welton speaking at the Green & Sustainable Chemistry conference (2019)"></img>
